    {
      "id": "research-scenarios-roadmap",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Use Cases, Migration Checklist, and Roadmap",
      "position": {
        "x": 1880,
        "y": 800
      },
      "width": 680,
      "height": 840,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "### Concrete Twilite Use Cases, Migration Checklist, and Roadmap\n\nScenario set:\n- graph-grounded AI assistance with constrained actions\n- semantic navigation and explanation paths\n- auto-clustering for workspace organization\n- change impact analysis on dependency-like relations\n- schema and ontology enforcement via node classes\n- collaboration and merge semantics modeled as graph constraints\n\nMigration checklist:\n- establish edge semantics and which subsets must remain acyclic\n- choose the primary graph model, likely a property graph baseline\n- treat modifications as append-only events\n- define separate UI, agent, and analytics query contracts\n- add indexes early for class, edge type, and key properties\n- build a benchmark harness before deep optimization\n\nRoadmap milestones:\n- graph semantics baseline\n- event-sourced change log\n- indexes plus query APIs\n- first user-visible graph algorithms\n- incremental analytics layer\n- storage backend evaluation and hardening\n",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false,
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
